# Example threat-intel feed. Rename to ja3_*.csv / ja4_*.csv / jarm_*.csv to load it.
# Lines starting with # are ignored.
#
# abuse.ch format: <hash>,<first_seen>,<last_seen>,<reason>
# simple format:   <fingerprint>,<label>[,<source>]
# bare format:     <fingerprint>
#
# The entries below are illustrative placeholders, NOT real intel — replace
# them with a downloaded feed (see README.md for sources).
#
# simple format example:
0000000000000000000000000000aaaa,Example Malware Family,my-feed
# abuse.ch format example:
0000000000000000000000000000bbbb,2024-01-01 00:00:00,2024-06-01 00:00:00,ExampleListingReason
